Class Elevator

java.lang.Object
ElevatorSubsystem.Elevator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class Elevator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
Elevator class which handles the state of an individual elevator along receiving and responding to messages from the ElevatorSystem
Author:
Harjap Gill, Jason Gao

      Parameters:

      departureTime - Initial time before wait begins (created by System.getCurrentTimeInMillis())
